      <div style="float: left; width: 50%;">
        <h2> The Birth of a New Culture </h2>
        <br />
        <p>
          Modni is a branch of the Fraser Valley Korean Art Society that focuses on bringing awareness to the issue of   bicultural identity, namely Korean Canadian identity, using various forms of art. At present, Modni consists of   a performance team specializing in playing Korean drums that has performed at numerous locations throughout the Greater Vancouver Area, as well as a budding media team and administrative team.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
