<section id="core-concepts" style="background-color: rgba(158,11,15,1);">
  <div class="center-block col-md-10" style="text-align: center; padding-top: 5%;">
    <h1 class="fWhite" style="font-size: 50px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 2%;">Core Concepts</h2>
    <hr class="hr fW" style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <h4 class="fWhite" style="margin-bottom: 10%;">
      At its core, Modni is essentially a thought experiment. We do not know exacty what we are looking for when we say “Korean-Canadian” culture, yet through these means, we hope to find any semblance of an answer.
    </h3>
    <div class="col-md-4 text-center post2" style="vetrical-align: top">
      <i class="fa fa-circle-o-notch fa-spin fa-3x fWhite"></i>
      <h3 class="fWhite" style="font-size: 25px; font-weight: 600">Arts</h3>
      <p style="display: inline-block; font-size: 15px; margin-top: 5%; margin-bottom: 8%;" class="fWhite">We have chosen art as our form of reflection and meditation on our experiences because of its expressive quality. At the forefront we have Korean traditional drumming fused with Western rhythms and instruments and soon will be working with videography as well. A multitude of art forms will be introduced as the year progresses.</p>
    </div><div class="col-md-4 text-center post2" style="vetrical-align: top">
      <i class="fa fa-gear fa-spin fa-3x fWhite"></i>
      <h3 class="fWhite" style="font-size: 25px; font-weight: 600">Cultural Identity</h3>
      <p style="display: inline-block; font-size: 15px; margin-top: 5%; margin-bottom: 8%" class="fWhite">If one were to define identity simply as a culmination of experience, then to understand one’s identity, we would need to reflect on our past experiences. In the case of cultural identity then, we would need to understand the experiences of those who also share our culture. Modni strives to be this connection.</p>
    </div><div class="col-md-4 text-center post2" style="vetrical-align: top">
      <i class="fa fa-refresh fa-spin fa-3x fWhite"></i>
      <h3 class="fWhite" style="font-size: 25px; font-weight: 600">Community</h3>
      <p style="display: inline-block; font-size: 15px; margin-top: 5%; margin-bottom: 8%;" class="fWhite">Half of Modni is to reach out to the public domain via art; the other half is entirely internal. Involving all talents is our method of building a community that will allow us to share our past experiences whilst creating new ones. To bridge our 2nd generation, Korean-Canadian, community with the 1st generation community, we must first understand our own culture and see where our differences lie.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center" style="padding-bottom: 20px;">
      <a class="btn btn-lg btn-default button" href="http://fvkas.com/contact-us/" style="margin-top: 5%;">Sign Up Now !</a>
      <br>
      <br>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
